vote.title: A resolution authorizing the execution of a mutual termination of lease agreement between the City of Dallas and Family Gateway, Inc. operating as Family Gateway Center for approximately 17,646 square feet of land and 22,500 square feet of building and improvements, located at 711 South Saint Paul Street, also known as 1722 Marilla Street, to be effective upon the execution of the mutual termination of lease agreement between the City and Family Gateway, Inc. - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
